## Definition of Done (applies to all stories)

- [ ] Code reviewed by at least one peer (PR approved)
- [ ] tsc / build passes (no compile errors)
- [ ] Tests pass: vitest / jest / pytest — zero failures
- [ ] jest-axe: 0 accessibility violations (UI stories only)
- [ ] APIM smoke test passes (API stories only)
- [ ] Evidence comment posted to ADO WI (test count, coverage, deployment URL)
- [ ] README updated with new capabilities
- [ ] No secrets or PATs in code

